sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant IDX as HistoricalFactsIndexer
    participant GEN as QuizGenerationService
    participant RAG as RAGQuizPipeline
    participant EMB as EmbeddingGenerator
    participant VDB as ChromaSportsStore
    participant NEWS as DuckDuckGoNewsSearch
    participant LLM as GeminiQuizGenerator
    participant PARSER as QuizResponseParser
    participant VALID as QuizValidator
    participant SESS as QuizSessionManager

    User->>UI: Select sport + difficulty, click Generate
    UI->>IDX: index_historical_facts() (first run if needed)
    IDX->>VDB: get_existing_ids()/upsert_facts()

    UI->>GEN: generate(sport, difficulty, include_news=True)
    GEN->>RAG: generate_quiz(...)
    RAG->>EMB: embed_texts([query])
    EMB-->>RAG: query_embedding
    RAG->>VDB: query_facts(query_embedding, top_k, sport, difficulty)
    VDB-->>RAG: historical_chunks
    RAG->>NEWS: search_latest_news(sport, limit)
    NEWS-->>RAG: news_results (or empty on failure)
    RAG->>LLM: generate_quiz_text(grounded_prompt)
    LLM-->>RAG: raw_response
    RAG-->>GEN: pipeline_result

    GEN->>PARSER: parse(raw_response)
    PARSER-->>GEN: QuizPayload
    GEN->>VALID: validate(payload, expected_*)
    VALID-->>GEN: valid
    GEN-->>UI: QuizGenerationResult

    UI->>SESS: set_current_quiz(payload)
    UI-->>User: Render questions + source context
    User->>UI: Submit answers
    UI->>SESS: submit_quiz()
    SESS-->>UI: score, total
    UI-->>User: Score + explanations + citations
